{"tid":2447381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸示威波及台商   外交部建議掛國旗區分","createTime":"2021-03-15T07:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T10:26:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"08345ccace08a2bba163088804b12529851b5de2","tid":2447381,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"緬甸示威昨天至少有38名示威者及1名警察身亡，部分緬甸民眾懷疑有中國背後勢力在資助軍方鎮壓平民，民間反中情緒逐漸高漲，當地中國工廠因此遭到縱火，台商也受到波及。外交部今（15）天表示，位於萊達雅工業區的台商企業「昌億公司」廠區昨晚被示威群眾包圍，且有10名台籍幹部一度受困。外交部今天建議台商以緬甸文字將廠區標示為「台灣企業」並懸掛我國國旗，避免示威民眾誤判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-03-15/549272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-03-15%2F549272&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=6f576c5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-03-15/549272</a>"},{"pid":"07bd76980dc06759fdbf129df307081ed7c8bc7f","tid":2447381,"uid":169529,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981b6f48f4852bbc6fabdd1f486e429ca6804316","tid":2447381,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:15:38.000Z","msg":"標示為台灣企業就可能冇事既<br />\n但又要掛支中國國旗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc9a468ee0fd32c75dfe9c936ddd74e2d66f242","tid":2447381,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"應該公佈大量中資工廠既地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b286b3038e718205d4875be5534eeefba7b55738","tid":2447381,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07bd76980dc06759fdbf129df307081ed7c8bc7f","tid":2447381,"uid":169529,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\"